'''Little Long Pond''' is a {{convert|45|acre|m2|sing=on}} pond in [[Wareham, Massachusetts|Wareham]] and [[Plymouth, Massachusetts]]. The pond is located east of the southeasternmost point of [[Myles Standish State Forest]] within [[Camp Cachalot]], southeast of [[Charge Pond]], southwest of [[Five Mile Pond (Plymouth, Massachusetts)|Five Mile Pond]], and south of [[Abner Pond]].

There is another '''[[Little Long Pond (Plymouth, Massachusetts)|Little Long Pond]]''' entirely within Plymouth's borders located north of [[Long Pond (Plymouth, Massachusetts)|Long Pond]] and [[Gallows Pond]].

